text: Sònia Carrancà Del Barco (born 7 February 1999) is an Andorran footballer who plays as a midfielder for Andorran-based Spanish Women's First Division of Catalonia club ENFAF. She has been a member of the Andorra women's national team. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers
